---
// Timeline.astro
---

<div class="timeline-container">
  <h3 class="timeline-title"><span class="marker-highlight">Consensus</span>: Engagement Strategy</h3>
  <div class="timeline">
    <div class="timeline-item sharp-border uneven-clip-1 skew-left interactive-hover">
      <div class="phase">Phase 1</div>
      <h4>Listening Sessions</h4>
      <p>Gathering feedback from Gowanus residents and local studio artists on traffic and congestion.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-item sharp-border uneven-clip-2 skew-right interactive-hover">
      <div class="phase">Phase 2</div>
      <h4>Design & Iteration</h4>
      <p>Collaborative workshops to outline the 'Art Spine' route, balancing safety and aesthetics.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-item sharp-border uneven-clip-1 skew-left interactive-hover">
      <div class="phase">Phase 3</div>
      <h4>Pilot Program</h4>
      <p>Temporary street closures and weekend art walks to test the impact of the spine.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-item sharp-border uneven-clip-2 skew-right interactive-hover">
      <div class="phase">Phase 4</div>
      <h4>Implementation</h4>
      <p>Permanent zoning adjustments and streetscaping for the full Gowanus Art Spine.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .timeline-container {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .timeline-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* The Line */
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 20px;
    width: var(--border-width);
    background-color: var(--color-dark);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    background-color: #fff;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-left: 40px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(even) {
    align-self: flex-end;
    margin-left: 0;
    margin-right: 40px;
  }

  .phase {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-item h4 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-item p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .timeline::before {
      left: 20px;
    }
    .timeline-item:nth-child(even) {
      align-self: flex-start;
      margin-left: 40px;
      margin-right: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
